data.description: This charming and spacious 1950's home is waiting for you. This home is on a huge corner lot.  The large fully fenced back yard is perfect for entertaining or just relaxing to the sound of the soothing water feature.  You can enjoy creating endless culinary delights in the large eat in kitchen, and enjoy in your casual dining area.  You would be only minutes away from the local park, community center and to public transportation. The large 2 car detached garage has plenty of storage space.  In the fully finished basement you will find an additional bedroom, wonderful office space, a bonus room ( currently used as a huge closet ) and a family room perfect for watching your favorite shows or just kicking back and relaxing.  You won't want to miss seeing this home.
